::{{DIcon|Exit}} Well, I'm heading off, then.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504060233-->
:::'''Eacus:''' The senior senators love saying, "We stand at the turning point of the Light Calendar." Maybe they're right. Goodbye. Hope we both make it through this turning point.
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
